<BR>
1-4 fight the newbie crap in kelethin<BR>
<BR>
5-8 fight the orcs on orc hill in greater faydark<BR>
<BR>
9-10 fight at crush bone<BR>
<BR>
11-13 fight at chess board in butcher block<BR>
<BR>
14-20 fight in oasis get in orc groups croc groups and all that stuff.<BR>
<BR>
21-28 fight the avaiks in south karana<BR>
<BR>
29- 35 get in spire groups and kill gnolls if you have good enough gear just solo them and use heal song after battles<BR>
<BR>
36-42 fight in overthere this place is great once you feal comfortable with your fear song just twist that with snare song.<BR>
<BR>
43-48 kill the dwarfs in butcher block. Try to get the ones at the beach spawn or docks. Now what you do is get charm up then charm one and attack the other with it repeat this proces till one of them is almost dead then switch your charm to there more healthy one and finish him with that then finish the one with dots. just put up two dots and selos and run around till he's dead twisting them. repeat process till 48.<BR>
 48-53 kill the spirocs in timourous deep use the same process as you used on the dwarfs. <BR>
53-55 go to karnors castle that place is great experience.<BR>
53-60 go to velkators lab<BR>
<BR>
Thats my guide and if you don;t like it i don't give a rats a$$.
