				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				For info on how much various instruments add to your songs (some songs *require an instrument* other songs are enhanced by them, and others are just sung, go to www.eqdiva.com there is a TON of great bard stuff there.<BR>
Also, there are degrees of insruments.  The ordinary flute you buy from a vendor has like 0% add to the song.  But the Flute of Eternal Night adds like 35% to the song, and this bad boy here is what you really want:<BR>
Agilmente's Flute of Flight  <BR>
[LORE] [MAGIC] [NO DROP] <BR>
<BR>
Skill: Wind   75% to songs <BR>
Description: Bard Quest Item (50) <BR>
Drop Location:<BR>
Quest(Test of Pitch) Plane of Air <BR>
Rarity: Rare <BR>
 <BR>
Go to eqdiva and look up the class, lots of great info there.<BR>
Peace,<BR>
Gileas Dreamsinger, bard of the 51st string
