				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				THE BARDS DETAILED GUIDE ON LVLS 1-15<BR>
<BR>
  first of all start a half elf bard theyre the best bards they have the second highest str wich will make your weight allowance highier and make you hit harder the highest dex witch effects how powerful your songs are have the second most sta and agi they have the least wis but wis isnt important to a bard<BR>
  start off in greater faydark (kelethin) the best hunting is there on lvls 1-5 hunt in the newbie area there and save up for leather armor but just the tunic leggings and cloak then get a rusty wepon off a decaying skeliton (1hs) and once youve dinged 4 u should put 20 points into smithing at your guild take that rusty wepon go to felwith at the soal of all haols there is a dwarf merchant up stairs she sels sharpening stones buy some use them to sharpen your rusty wepon at a forge after that you should hunt at orc hill lvls 6-9 and save up for bronze armor and a velium sword on lvl 10 get a group go to crush bone and hunt at trainer hill once you ding 11 you can go to the chess board in butch block mountains and solo 1 skeloton at a time but be careful youre kill on seen to everything there and if something goes wrong you can always sing your lvl 5 song and run to safty (zone) once you ding 15 you can hunt at the aqua goblin camps easily everything there will be green to you but each goblin drops about 3pp each so its a good way to make money save up for plate its expense but weighs less then bronze <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
by lvl 15 and if you listened to this guide and met its goal this should be what you acheve <BR>
<BR>
equtiment list<BR>
<BR>
silver amber ring = 2str<BR>
a 2dex ring<BR>
a black steel rap = 6ac 10 hp<BR>
a full set of plate armor<BR>
a veluim sword<BR>
<BR>
skills<BR>
<BR>
smithing mastered<BR>
<BR>
during all this you should...<BR>
<BR>
get all your songs and insturments<BR>
and mastering smithinmg to make banded armor<BR>
afterwards <BR>
<BR>
after you acheved this you should master brewing then tailoring and get a second sword to duelweild at 20 your velium sword will proc and lvl up and eventaully get steel singing armor<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
innorruk server<BR>
lvl 14 bard<BR>
melidee               thanks for reading
